(11, '2015_01_04_11_21_58local_tour2014_03.jpg', 'Asia Euro University Takes Technology into Consideration', 'សាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបយកបច្ចេកវិទ្យាចូលទៅក្នុងការពិចារណ', 'Asia Euro University Takes Technology into Consideration', 'សាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបយកបច្ចេកវិទ្យាចូលទៅក្នុងការពិចារណ', '<p><span style="color: rgb(66, 139, 202); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.1;">Asia Euro University Takes Technology into Consideration</span></p>\n<div class="description text-justify" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;"><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/seminar2013_16.jpg" alt="" width="400" class="img-responsive imgisleft" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; float: left;" />Due to ASEAN Integration 2015, Asia Euro University has updated its own curriculum and professional skills, particularly in technology, in order to respond to job markets today. Furthermore, AEU has taken into serious consideration for training and promoting staff, lecturers and students with technical workshop by professional experts.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">For instance, on February 23, 2013, Asia Euro University conducted one seminar on World-Recognized IT Study Program and Smartphone Technology Today. The seminar was attended by Cisco Networking Academy Program manager in Cambodia Laos and Myanmar; Manager of programming and Manager of Product Technology as presenters, as well as lecturers, staff and students.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">Mr. Chhoeun Savorn, Vice Rector of Asia Euro University, said in the greeting session that the seminar was mainly focused on Cisco Networking Academy, Smartphone, and Cloud Technology and sharing experience by the experts who are from well-known companies. In addition, Cisco has a lot of companies and organizations&nbsp; as its partners such as Campura, First Cambodia, Ly Solutions, and Organization for Emergent Talent (OET). Those partners collaborated with AEU and exhibited their own products and announced job vacancy to AEU students. Mr. Chhoeun Savorn addressed that the content of the seminar not only was beneficial to staff, lecturers and all students who participated in the seminar but also others who joined via Cisco WebEx in the whole country. Cisco WebEx is firstly used for such a seminar in Cambodia and it is also supported by Cisco Singapore and other companies which provide internal internet service.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">Similarly, Mr. Long Chhunhour, Product Manager of Cisco System Company in Cambodia, raised some advantages of using Cisco WebEx technology which enables distant meeting, seminars, workshops, or conferences to be run smoothly. This is the purpose of Cisco whose aim is to help develop human resources and to provide opportunities for students, government and other organizations in order to contact each other (99%). Mr. Chhunhour added that IT is a prime major that enables economics to be developed. In fact, Cisco is one of the wellknown companies in the world and it provides students, whose major is IT, with well-paid job opportunities and worldwide-certificate recognition. As a result, students should smartly choose any institution with Cisco license which results quality of IT training. In connection with IT, Mr. Hong Sophany, Programming Manager of Cisco in Cambodia, in Laos, in Myanmar; briefly stated about the background of Cisco which invented Cisco Networking Academy (CNA) for E-learning, and it aims to help develop human resources over the world without fee. CNA has better developed itself than before. Consequently, this network has been run on Smartphone or Tablet. Finally, Mr. Hong Sophany addressed that the ones who hold Cisco certificate can apply for jobs in countries in the world, such as Malaysia or Singapore.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">Next, Mr. Kim Yoeurn, Deputy General Director of First Cambodia, made an impression of poor today-technology human resources. He added that is the main concern when ASEAN is integrated in 2015. In terms of the integration, his company as well as his partner, Cisco, promotes technology human resources and students development. Particularly, AEU students are given training opportunities at his company because he has a lot of branches in many countries such as Laos, Myanmar and Vietnam.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">In addition, Mr. Kim Meng, General Manager of KALICEE SOLUTION Co., Ltd, shared his knowledge and experience relevant to programming in Smartphone. He gave some background of developing phone''s programming, proposed some key concept to become a successful programmer and raised some benefits of programming which is being used in worldwide.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">In connection with technology, Mr. Sith Borin, Database Administrator of Asia Euro University, share his new knowledge of using database and information via internet system known as Cloud Technology. He demonstrated how to use technology and techniques for share program, data, or&nbsp; information and how to recall using data via internet of the companies which serve such a service&mdash;Cloud Technology &mdash;SkyDrive, iCloud, Google Drive, and Dropbox.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">Moreover, Mr. Sith Borin addressed that those companies manage to restore data on a limit scale whose data is able to be recalled using through Smartphone or Tablet.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">After demonstrating, all speakers invited questions from trainees and answered all questions to the trainees at AEU and the trainees&nbsp; via Cisco WebEx. After that, they visited&nbsp; exhibited products from their own partners.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;">It is remarked that Asia Euro University with Cisco Company in Cambodia, Laos and Myanmar takes technology in consideration and promotes the technology in IT curriculum as well as all majors in Computer field which enables students to study with Cisco Networking. It is clear that Asia Euro University has already developed itself in order to get students to compete job markets when ASEAN is integrated in 2015.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: left;"><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/seminar2013_17.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" />&nbsp;<img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/seminar2013_18.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" />&nbsp;<img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/seminar2013_19.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" /></p>\n</div>', '<p>សាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបយកបច្ចេកវិទ្យាចូលទៅក្នុងការពិចារណ</p>\n<div class="description text-justify" style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px;">\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 22.796875px;"><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/seminar2013_16.jpg" alt="" width="400" class="img-responsive imgisleft" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; float: left;" /></p>\n<div>ដោយសារការធ្វើសមាហរណកម្មអាស៊ានឆ្នាំ 2015 សាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបបានធ្វើឱ្យទាន់សម័យនូវជំនាញវិជ្ជាជីវៈនិងកម្មវិធីសិក្សារបស់ខ្លួនជាពិសេសនៅក្នុងបច្ចេកវិទ្យាដើម្បីឆ្លើយតបទ