INSERT INTO `tblnews` (`nid`, `en_title`, `kh_title`, `en_short_desc`, `kh_short_desc`, `en_long_desc`, `kh_long_desc`, `cat_id`, `thumbnial`, `uid`, `date`) VALUES
(1, 'AEU''s Students Took Study Tour to the Seaside Resorts of Cambodia', 'និស្សិតអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុប បានយកដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សា នៅរមណីយដ្ឋានឆ្នេរសមុទ្រ នៃប្រទេសកម្ពុជា', 'The 62 students from the Faculty of Science and Technology of Asia Euro University were selected to take a study tour, from March 29 to March 30, 2014, to Kompot and Sihanuokville seaside.', 'សិស្ស 62 ពីមហាវិទ្យាល័យវិទ្យាសាស្រ្តនិងបច្ចេកវិទ្យានៃសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបត្រូវបានជ្រើសរើសដើម្បីយកដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សាមួយពីថ្ងៃទី 29 ខែមីនាដល់ខែមីនា 30, 2014 ដើម្បីកំពតព្រះស៊ីហនុនិងតំបន់មាត់សមុទ្រ។', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;"><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_02.jpg" alt="" width="400" class="img-responsive imgisleft" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; float: left;" />The 62 students from the Faculty of Science and Technology of Asia Euro University were selected to take a study tour, from March 29 to March 30, 2014, to Kompot and Sihanuokville seaside.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">The study tour departed from Phnom Penh to Kompot province and went on to Sihanoukville province. Crossing both Kompot province and Sihanoukville, the students would take study tour in Kompot city, Bokor Resort (Borkor Paradise Resort) and Sihanoukville seaside. The study tour was organized to respond the university''s requirement, research skill development.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">The study tour is aimed to make students search and understand seaside tour sites in Kompot and Sihaoukville. The tour sites are considered as both the most beautiful bay in the world and the most beautiful place for students to take a rest.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">In order to achieve the study tour''s objectives, Asia Euro University will organize a challenging game, called ''Going toward Kompot Province and Sihanoukville Seaside of Cambodia'', for the students. With the game, the students had to search for information relevant to each seaside resort as mentioned above, use an appropriate transportation to the target area, search available accommodation, guesthouses, hotels, and restaurants by utilizing the data from the Internet and using Software Google. As a result, three challenging groups were awarded by cash from Asia Euro University and SIDS Company.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">Remarkably, the students pursuing IT at Asia Euro University are annually transferred to take both a local and foreign study tour. In fact, Asia Euro University collaborates with Singapore, Malaysia, and China.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px;"><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_03.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" />&nbsp;<img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_04.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" />&nbsp;<img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_05.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />\n&nbsp;</p>', '<p>&nbsp;<img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_02.jpg" alt="" width="400" class="img-responsive imgisleft" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15.1199998855591px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; float: left; display: inline-block !important;" /></p>\n<div>សិស្ស 62 ពីមហាវិទ្យាល័យវិទ្យាសាស្រ្តនិងបច្ចេកវិទ្យានៃសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបត្រូវបានជ្រើសរើសដើម្បីយកដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សាមួយពីថ្ងៃទី 29 ខែមីនាដល់ខែមីនា 30, 2014 ដើម្បីកំពតព្រះស៊ីហនុនិងតំបន់មាត់សមុទ្រ។</div>\n<div>ដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សានេះបានចាកចេញពីទីក្រុងភ្នំពេញទៅខេត្តកំពតហើយបានទៅខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ។ ឆ្លងកាត់ខេត្តកំពតទាំងពីរនិងក្រុងព្រះសីហនុសិស្សនឹងទទួលយកដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សានៅក្រុងកំពត, រមណីយដ្ឋានបូកគោ (Borkor រមណីយដ្ឋានឋានសួគ៌) និងតំបន់មាត់សមុទ្រខេត្តព្រះសីហនុ។ ដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សានេះត្រូវបានរៀបចំឡើងដើម្បីឆ្លើយតបតម្រូវការអភិវឌ្ឍជំនាញស្រាវជ្រាវសាកលវិទ្យាល័យនេះ។</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>ដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សានេះគឺមានគោលបំណងដើម្បីធ្វើឱ្យនិស្សិតស្វែងរកនិងការយល់ដឹងពីដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចនៅតំបន់មាត់សមុទ្រតំបន់បណ្ដាញនៅកំពតនិង Sihaoukville ។ វិបសាយដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចនេះត្រូវបានចាត់ទុកថាជាទាំងពីរច្រកដ៏ស្រស់ស្អាតបំផុតក្នុងពិភពលោកនិងជាកន្លែងដ៏ស្រស់ស្អាតបំផុតសម្រាប់សិស្សនិស្សិតដើម្បីទទួលយកការសម្រាកមួយ។</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>ក្នុងគោលបំណងដើម្បីសម្រេចបាននូវគោលបំណងទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សារបស់សាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបនឹងរៀបចំជាការប្រកួតដ៏លំបាកដែលហៅថា &quot;ទៅទៅរកខេត្តកំពតនិងខេត្តព្រះសីហនុឆ្នេរសមុទ្រនៃប្រទេសកម្ពុជាសម្រាប់សិស្ស។ ជាមួយនឹងការប្រកួតនេះសិស្សបានដើម្បីស្វែងរកព័ត៌មានពាក់ព័ន្ធនឹងរមណីយដ្ឋានមាត់សមុទ្រគ្នាដូចដែលបានរៀបរាប់ខាងលើ, ប្រើការដឹកជញ្ជូនសមស្របទៅតំបន់គោលដៅការស្វែងរកកន្លែងស្នាក់នៅដែលអាចរកបាន, ផ្ទះសំណាក់, សណ្ឋាគារ, ភោជនីយដ្ឋាននិងដោយប្រើប្រាស់ទិន្នន័យពីអ៊ីនធឺណិតនិងការប្រើប្រាស់កម្មវិធីរបស់ Google ។ ជាលទ្ធផលក្រុមចំនួនបីនាក់ត្រូវបានប្រគល់ជូនដោយលំបាកសាច់ប្រាក់ពីសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបនិងក្រុមហ៊ុន SIDS ។</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>គួរឱ្យកត់សម្គាល់សិស្សបន្តការសិក្សាផ្នែក IT នៅសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបត្រូវបានផ្ទេរជារៀងរាល់ឆ្នាំដើម្បីយកទាំងពីរដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សាមួយក្នុងស្រុកនិងបរទេស។ ជាការពិតសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបសហការជាមួយប្រទេសសិង្ហបុរីម៉ាឡេស៊ីនិងប្រទេសចិន។</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div><span>&nbsp;</span><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_03.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15.1199998855591px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block !important;" /><span style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15.1199998855591px;">&nbsp;</span><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_04.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15.1199998855591px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block !important;" /><span style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15.1199998855591px;">&nbsp;</span><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2014/local_tour2014_05.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15.1199998855591px; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block !important;" /></div>', 1, '2015_01_04_07_51_27local_tour2014_03.jpg', 1, '2015-01-14 16:07:48'),
(2, 'The Student-delegation of Asia Euro University Pays a Study Visit to Singapore', 'នេះជាសិស្ស-គណៈប្រតិភូនៃសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបសងទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សាទៅកាន់ប្រទេសសិង្ហបុរី', 'In response to the study-tour invitation extended by the Institute of Technical Education of Singapore, Mr. Chhoeung Savorn, Vice-rector of Asia Euro University; Mr. Bou Chhun, Head of Information Technology; and Mr. Khan Sokha, Head of Computer and Science led AEU''s student-delegation, totally 12, to take study tour to Singapore.', 'ការឆ្លើយតបទៅនឹងការអញ្ជើញ n ការសិក្សាដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ច-បានពង្រីកដោយវិទ្យាស្ថានអប់រំបច្ចេកទេសនៃប្រទេសសិង្ហបុរីលោកឈឿងសាវន, អនុសាកលវិទ្យាធិការនៃសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបបាន; លោកប៊ូឈុនជាប្រធានបច្ចេកវិទ្យាព័ត៌មាន! និងលោកខាន់សុខាប្រធានកុំព្យូទ័រនិងវិទ្យាសាស្រ្តបានដឹកនាំគណៈប្រតិភូអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបសិស្ស-របស់ទាំងស្រុង 12 ដើម្បីទទួលបានដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សាទៅកាន់ប្រទេសសិង្ហបុរី។', '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;"><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/visit_ite2013_02.jpg" alt="" width="400" class="img-responsive imgisleft" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block !important; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; float: left;" />In response to the study-tour invitation extended by the Institute of Technical Education of Singapore, Mr. Chhoeung Savorn, Vice-rector of Asia Euro University; Mr. Bou Chhun, Head of Information Technology; and Mr. Khan Sokha, Head of Computer and Science led AEU''s student-delegation, totally 12, to take study tour to Singapore.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">After arriving at Phnom Penh International Airport in the evening of October 18th, 2013, Mr. Chhoeung Savorn, Chief of the delegation, said that the students of Computer Science and Hotel and Tourism Management, totally 8, and 1 lecturer of tourism were selected to pay a oneweek -study visit to Singapore. The study tour began from October 12th to October 18th, 2013. In addition, he said that our student-delegation absorbed a lot of knowledge and experience from Singaporean education system; in particular, Computer Design, Mobile Application, VoIP, Cloud Computing, Electricity, Electronic, Film Making, Video Design, Lab Management, Computer Management, Hotel Management, Hotel Management, Cooking Skill, and Hospitality. Besides paying a study visit to the Institute of Technical Education of Singapore, AEU student-delegation was invited to visit other companies and technically trained with famous companies such as EMC and IExperience at iDA. Those companies have a lot of branches in Singapore. Furthermore, the student-delegation was invited to visit potential tourist sites of Singapore.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">Mr. Chhoeung Savorn said that Asia Euro&nbsp; University is proud of taking study tour to Singapore. He had a meeting with Management Board of the Institution of Technology Education; in particular, with Ms Denise Tan, Director of Hospitality, in order to discuss the study exchange of hospitality between both countries. As a result, after the meeting, Ms Danise Tan agreed on the study exchange of tourism. This agreement will be officially launched until the new building (Golden Building with 15 storeys) of Asia Euro University will have been constructed in 2014. The new building consists of thevariety of lab rooms of tourism and restaurant section for doing practicum. Under directing by H.E Doung Leang, Rector of Asia Euro University, and other management board, Asia Euro University has developed itself and grown dramatically. One more thing is that Asia Euro University has been collaborating with other countries as its own partners in order to provide and promote AEU''s students with good opportunities to absorb certain knowledge and qualify good performance.</p>\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; padding: 0px 22.796875px; text-align: justify;">Miss. Chea Puthearith, the representative of AEU''s students expressed her own interests and joy of the study tour and raised some benefits of her study tour to Singapore. The study tour is just the capital of further study encouragement because we have good opportunities to see the developments of the country, Singapore. Therefore, it is the force to push and encourage us to further learn and search in order to become qualified human resources who enable to develop country. Most importantly, both knowledge and experience we absorbed will share to other AEE''s students. Also, Miss. Chea Puthearith suggested that all students should work hard on their own major upgrade communicative languages due to ASEAN integration in 2015 and job market competition.</p>\n<p><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/visit_ite2013_03.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block !important;" /><span style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em;">&nbsp;</span><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/visit_ite2013_04.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block !important;" /><span style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em;">&nbsp;</span><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/visit_ite2013_05.jpg" alt="" width="360" class="img-responsive" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 0.9em; line-height: 1.4em; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: inline-block !important;" />&nbsp;</p>', '<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<p><img src="http://aeu.edu.kh/media/tinymce/uploads/pictures/news_event/2013/visit_ite2013_02.jpg" alt="" width="400" class="img-responsive imgisleft" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15.1199998855591px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin: 10px 10px 10px 0px; float: left; display: inline-block !important;" /></p>\n<div>ក្នុងការឆ្លើយតបទៅនឹងការអញ្ជើញការសិក្សាដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ច-បានពង្រីកដោយវិទ្យាស្ថានអប់រំបច្ចេកទេសនៃប្រទេសសិង្ហបុរីលោកឈឿងសាវន, អនុសាកលវិទ្យាធិការនៃសាកលវិទ្យាល័យអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបបាន; លោកប៊ូឈុនជាប្រធានបច្ចេកវិទ្យាព័ត៌មាន! និងលោកខាន់សុខាប្រធានកុំព្យូទ័រនិងវិទ្យាសាស្រ្តបានដឹកនាំគណៈប្រតិភូអាស៊ីអឺរ៉ុបសិស្ស-របស់ទាំងស្រុង 12 ដើម្បីទទួលបានដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សាទៅកាន់ប្រទេសសិង្ហបុរី។</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>បន្ទាប់ពីបានមកដល់ព្រលានយន្តហោះអន្តរជាតិភ្នំពេញនៅថ្ងៃទី 18 ខែតុលាល្ងាចឆ្នាំ 2013 លោកឈឿងសាវនប្រធានគណៈប្រតិភូបាននិយាយថានិស្សិតនៃវិទ្យាសាស្រ្តកុំព្យូទ័រនិងគ្រប់គ្រងសណ្ឋាគារនិងទេសចរណ៍ទាំងស្រុង 8 និង 1 សាស្ត្រាចារ្យនៃវិស័យទេសចរណ៍ត្រូវបានគេជ្រើសរើសឱ្យ បង់ដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ច -study oneweek ទៅប្រទេសសឹង្ហបុរី។ ដំណើរទស្សនកិច្ចសិក្សានេះបានចាប់ផ្តើមពីទី 12 ខែតុលាដល់ថ្ងៃទី 18 ខែតុលាឆ្នាំ 2013 លើសពីនេះទៀតគាត់បាននិយាយថាសិស្ស-គណៈប្រតិភូរបស់យើងបានស្រូបយកច្រើននៃចំណេះដឹងនិងបទពិសោធពីប្រព័ន្ធអប់រំសឹង្ហបុរីមួយ ជាពិសេសការរចនាកុំព្យូទ័រ, កម្មវិធីទូរស័ព្ទ, សេវាកម្ម VoIP, កុំព្យូទ័រពពក, អគ្គីសនីអេឡិចត្រូនិ, ការធ្វើភាពយន្ត, វីដេ